{"tid":2258544,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本人誠邀潘太在萬聖節輕鬆一下，參與活動","createTime":"2020-10-26T06:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T07:27:21.000Z","uid":231886,"like":28,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"730d781cf1bbd7009bcd15e5e4aa252f3b7fe59a","tid":2258544,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:24:21.000Z","msg":"致潘太<br />\n<br />\n本人屌你，現誠邀潘太你出席萬聖節活動，與手足們同樂。<br />\n<br />\n詳情如下：<br />\n活動名稱: 哈囉喂泰驚萬聖節<br />\n                  (Halloween scare thai you)<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span class=\"x-large\">活動時間: 10月31日(Halloween)夜晚7點-10點</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">活動地點: 五區(旺角、中環、銅鑼灣、沙田、調景嶺將軍澳坑口寶琳)</span><br />\n<br />\n活動定位: 主題為泰國，支持泰國手足。此活動並非大型聚人活動，不聚人，而且係和理非活動。<br />\n<br />\n點解要搞依個活動？<br />\n<br />\n依家香港抗爭陷入樽頸，需要一啲創新活動。另外，今年Halloween啱啱好遇到泰國抗爭，泰國手足需要國際嘅關注同支持，此活動用一個唔同嘅方式表態同向泰國政府示威，諷刺巴育，而且增加港人對泰國示威嘅關注。最後，依家大規模聚人示威遊行聚到人嘅可能性低，且成本高，需要試下其他新形式同較低風險嘅活動，be water。<br />\n<br />\n活動流程:  參與者同我哋嘅義工會喺五區戴住巴育恐怖版面具(我哋會將面具嘅原檔擺上grp，希望大家都會一齊戴)另外，一啲關於泰國抗爭嘅物件會放置喺唔同checkpoint，checkpoint入面都有唔同嘅嘢拎！見到巴育或者checkpoint物件之後(詳細地點不會被公佈，要自己搵)影低佢擺上唔同嘅社交媒體(例如Twitter,IG)然後tag #MilkTeaAlliance，#StandWithThailand，#halloweenthaiscareyou，#หยุดคุกคามประชาชน，然後答啱佢問你關於泰國抗爭嘅問題，仲有糖同其他神秘嘢收！希望大家喺唔同地方(唔一定喺指定嘅五區)戴上巴育面具遍地開花！<br />\n<br />\n備註: 本活動沒有任何party成份。建議參加者戴唔同嘅面具同萬聖節裝扮加強氣氛，關於時政就更加好，亦都希望舉起三大訴求手勢聲援泰國手足。<br />\n<br />\n上年我哋係唔同社交平台都被質疑為鬼，但努力同成果有目共睹。希望大家停止捉鬼，要捉鬼嘅嚟我哋活動捉飽佢。😤<br />\n<br />\n人心比鬼更可怕！<br />\n<br />\n如果有任何意見、查詢、問題，請加入公海討論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/halloweenthaiscareyougrp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhalloweenthaiscareyougrp&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=eaada233\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/halloweenthaiscareyougrp</a><br />\n<br />\n關於活動嘅最新消息請參考此channel:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/halloweenthaiscareyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhalloweenthaiscareyou&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=c244facc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/halloweenthaiscareyou</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n祝 身體健康<br />\n屌你 上<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c8L09H5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc8L09H5.jpg&h=d9fac4f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Mj1T9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Mj1T9b.jpg&h=12e40707&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9e16323584d015ebb0d013dc04b9b60d52b9064","tid":2258544,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />齊來萬聖節"},{"pid":"d4d3eefa15e110dbbe798bf420f840eda17d9ae3","tid":2258544,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:25:49.000Z","msg":"無送頭啦"},{"pid":"42159e7a8648657779cbe86c716bc540beb27177","tid":2258544,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />太早無人回"},{"pid":"30a4207ea598823f215e26b05286111aebc834d0","tid":2258544,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97264f127a24338f9ee766ccc9be328832a81845","tid":2258544,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30a4207ea598823f215e26b05286111aebc834d0","tid":2258544,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:33:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />善心打破0回覆"},{"pid":"6dc6ad0431dae85f6ee930dc6bd5af5cbd27ceae","tid":2258544,"uid":243537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:34:44.000Z